    orig_stderr = sys.stderr

    sys.stderr = stream
    yield

def test_withPycharmNonTTYOverride(self):
        non_tty = StreamNonTTY()
        with pycharm(), replace_by(non_tty):
            self.assertFalse(is_a_tty(non_tty))
